{
  "id": "6a4bc614b769dc43875860d5",
  "title": "燃油サーチャージ",
  "created": 1783350805,
  "updated": 1783351120,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a4bc614b769dc43875860d5",
      "text": "燃油サーチャージ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350805,
      "updated": 1783350805
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc6150000000000fe46cd",
      "text": "燃料とする石油（ケロシン、軽油、重油など）の価格に追随する、運賃とは別建てで徴収される料金のこと",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350806,
      "updated": 1783350827
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc6740000000000fe46db",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350900,
      "updated": 1783350900
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc66a0000000000fe46da",
      "text": "別称",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350891,
      "updated": 1783350900
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc6800000000000fe46e3",
      "text": " [燃料サーチャージ]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350913,
      "updated": 1783350913
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc6690000000000fe46d9",
      "text": " [燃油特別付加運賃]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350889,
      "updated": 1783350995
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc6770000000000fe46dc",
      "text": " [燃料油価格変動調整金]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350903,
      "updated": 1783350996
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc6790000000000fe46dd",
      "text": " [燃料加算金]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350905,
      "updated": 1783350997
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc67a0000000000fe46de",
      "text": " [燃料課徴金]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350906,
      "updated": 1783350999
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc61e0000000000fe46ce",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350814,
      "updated": 1783350814
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc61e0000000000fe46cf",
      "text": "[燃料価格]の急激な変動により設定時の運賃では燃料代が賄えない事態に対応する措置",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350814,
      "updated": 1783351089
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc6af0000000000fe46f4",
      "text": "海運業界が1970年代から導入し、2000年代には航空、陸運業界にも広まった",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350959,
      "updated": 1783350961
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc61e0000000000fe46d0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350814,
      "updated": 1783350814
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc61e0000000000fe46d3",
      "text": "電気料金、ガス料金にも燃料の価格変動を料金に反映させるための追加徴収があり、[原料費調整制度]と呼ばれる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350814,
      "updated": 1783350990
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bc6960000000000fe46f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783350934,
      "updated": 1783350934
    },
